author: Y Combinator
description:
Yesterday, Boom (YC W16) made history. They successfully broke the sound barrier (3 times!) with XB-1, the first civil supersonic jet made in America.

Congrats to Blake Scholl, Chief Test Pilot Tristan “Gepetto” Brandenburg, and the entire Boom team!
title: America’s First Civil Supersonic Jet to Break the Sound Barrier
